::KitKat::

She looked at Megatron and the other bot. "You said to come alone. 
But you brought another bot with you. Is this how you wish to build a 
trust between us?"

She stood a little ways away from them, so she could run incase of 
trouble. She looked at Megatron. She opened her link to Destructor. A 
one way link, just so he could hear what was said, but not respond.
